content: I feel a mix of both. I'm excited to start reconnecting with others and taking steps towards improving my social life, but I'm also a bit nervous about how people will respond or if I'll be able to keep up with my goal. I've been out of the social loop for a while, so it's natural to feel a bit uncertain. However, I'm determined to take it one step at a time and focus on making progress, rather than worrying about the outcome.
